# Shell scripts are COPY'd into Linux containers and exec'd by /bin/sh.
# CRLF terminators make the kernel look for `/bin/sh\r` and the container
# crash-loops with "no such file or directory". Force LF regardless of a
# Windows clone's core.autocrlf setting.
*.sh text eol=lf
docker-entrypoint.sh text eol=lf

# The nginx config template is COPY'd into the image and marker-spliced by
# an awk exact-line match in docker-entrypoint.sh (`$0 == "# {{SCION_MAPS}}"`).
# A CRLF terminator makes the line `...}}\r`, the exact-match silently fails,
# and every per-Scion /morpheus + /ws/telemetry route vanishes (falls through
# to the SPA fallback → "<!DOCTYPE" instead of JSON). Force LF.
nginx.conf.template text eol=lf
*.template text eol=lf
*.conf text eol=lf
